I enjoy interacting with Singaporeans from all walks of life and listening to the narratives of their everyday needs and challenges. I am also a firm believer of youth empowerment and developing potentials, for they are the change-makers of the future.

In my personal time, I enjoy engaging in intellectual discussions with my peers from various disciplines, with topics ranging from current affairs to ethics and general life philosophies. I also enjoy keeping an active lifestyle through sports and regular runs.
